OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FA man who killed a mother of four in a
OL,7,F"catastrophic collision" while driving
OL,8,Fat double the speed limit while using
OL,9,Fnitrous oxide, has been jailed for 14
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FMohammed Irshad, 36, was driving a
OL,13,FMercedes on June 22, 2024 when he
OL,14,Fpulled out into the path of oncoming
OL,15,Ftraffic to overtake another car.
OL,17,FKenneth Kimblin was driving with his
OL,18,Fwife on St Helens Road in Bolton when
OL,19,Fthe crash happened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
