OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FKaren Kimblin, 63 died from her
OL,7,Finjuries. The former nurse was
OL,8,Fdescribed by her family as having "a
OL,9,Floving, caring nature" which also left
OL,10,Fher husband of 43 years seriously
OL,11,Finjured
OL,13,FIrshad, was described as an
OL,14,F"aggressive" and "furious" driver who
OL,15,Fthe court heard, gave a "callous"
OL,16,Fresponse to police after he was
OL,17,Farrested, saying: "How was it me that
OL,18,Fcaused the death?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
