OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FA judge who sentenced him said Irshad
OL,7,Fhad made "denials and minimalisations"
OL,8,Fto the Probation Service during the
OL,9,Flegal process.
OL,11,FBut at an earlier hearing, he pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to charges of causing death by
OL,13,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,14,Finjuries by driving. At Bolton Crown
OL,15,FCourt, he was jailed for 10 years and
OL,16,Fsix months, and banned from driving
OL,17,Ffor 12 years.
OL,19,FThe court heard two days before the
OL,20,Fcollision, Irshad was arrested on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of possession of cocaine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
