OL,6,FThe court heard St Helens Road is
OL,7,Flined with residential and commercial
OL,8,Fproperties with a 30mph limit in
OL,9,Fforce. The area was busy with traffic
OL,10,Fand pedestrians at the time, just
OL,11,Fbefore 7pm.
OL,13,FFather-of-two Irshad had a passenger
OL,14,Fin the Mercedes who was also injured
OL,15,Fin the crash, the court was told. The
OL,16,Fmanner of his driving was said to have
OL,17,Fgot progressively worse, from
OL,18,F"erratic" to "more aggressive".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
