OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FJudge Close said: "You were travelling
OL,7,Fsomewhere in the region of twice the
OL,8,Fspeed limit."
OL,10,FIrshad, of no fixed address, overtook
OL,11,Fa Toyota, forcing a moped and an SUV
OL,12,Fto take "evasive action".
OL,14,FHe then "moved completely into the
OL,15,Fpath" of oncoming traffic. His
OL,16,Factions, said Judge Close, gave Mr and
OL,17,FMrs Kimblin "no option to avoid" what
OL,18,Fhe called a "catastrophic collision".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
