OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FThe Nissan was flipped into the air
OL,7,Fand hit a wall, with three pedestrians
OL,8,Fsaid to have been near at the time.
OL,9,FJudge Close said: "Fortune alone
OL,10,Fprevented further tragedy."
OL,12,FThe couple were both cut free from the
OL,13,Fwreckage. Mr Kimblin, who the court
OL,14,Fheard was already an amputee, suffered
OL,15,F"serious and long-term injuries".
OL,17,FIn a victim impact statement, he said
OL,18,Fhe was "consumed by fear for his wife"
OL,19,Fin the immediate aftermath.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
