OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FFollowing the sentence Mr Kimblin
OL,7,Fsaid: "To this day, I still can't
OL,8,Fbelieve that I'll never see Karen
OL,9,Fagain. We were married for 43 years
OL,10,Fand had so many plans for our future
OL,11,Ftogether, but all that has been
OL,12,Fcruelly ripped away.
OL,14,F"Karen was the greatest thing that
OL,15,Fhappened to me, and she was very
OL,16,Fhighly thought of by everyone who had
OL,17,Fthe pleasure of meeting her. She was
OL,18,Fthe most loving and caring woman, and
OL,19,Fa beloved mum and grandma."
