OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FJudge Close told Irshad: "In his
OL,7,Fwords, you have left him lonely." One
OL,8,Fof her daughters meanwhile, who was
OL,9,Fpregnant at the time, said his driving
OL,10,Fhad "robbed" her of a mother.
OL,12,F"Yours was a deliberate decision to
OL,13,Fignore the rules of the road," Judge
OL,14,FClose told Irshad.
OL,16,F"You were travelling at around twice
OL,17,Fthe legal limit when you pulled into
OL,18,Foncoming traffic that was clear to be
OL,19,Fseen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
