OL,3,C'Erratic' and 'aggressive driver'
OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FIrshad has eight previous convictions
OL,7,Ffor 10 offences, including violence.
OL,9,FIn a tribute at the time, Mrs
OL,10,FKimblin's family said they were
OL,11,F'crushed' by her loss. "Karen worked
OL,12,Fall of her life as a nurse caring for
OL,13,Fothers, which came so easily to her
OL,14,Fwith her caring and loving nature,"
OL,15,Fthey said.
OL,17,F"Our family loves her beyond words and
OL,18,Freceived the same love and devotion in
OL,19,Freturn from her. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
