OL,4,Cjailed after mum-of-four dies
OL,6,FDetective Constable Aarron Cramer,
OL,7,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police's
OL,8,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Irshad's actions resulted in an
OL,10,Finnocent member of the public losing
OL,11,Ftheir life in this tragic collision.
OL,12,FOur thoughts remain with Karen's loved
OL,13,Fones.
OL,15,F"It is believed that Irshad was using
OL,16,Fnitrous oxide when he was driving
OL,17,Fwhich is totally unacceptable, drink
OL,18,Fand drug driving are part of our
OL,19,F'Fatal Four' main causes of death, and
OL,20,Fthis is another tragic but avoidable
OL,21,Foutcome for all involved.
